cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.CL. 

This paper is about object and part segmentation in computer vision, which is a subfield of computer vision and image processing. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a deep learning approach, which suggests that it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves semantic segmentation, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
